    "19": {
      "type": "markdown",
      "title": "",
      "content": "# \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f SRE / Developer View\nReliability engineering \u2014 **errors**, **latency**, **retry storms**, **fallbacks**, and **rate-limit headroom** across both services."
    },
    "20": {
      "type": "data",
      "title": "LLM error rate over time (%)",
      "query": "fetch spans | filter isNotNull(gen_ai.request.model) | makeTimeseries total = count(), errors = countIf(span.status_code == \"ERROR\") | fieldsAdd error_rate_pct = (errors[] / total[]) * 100",
      "visualization": "lineChart",
      "visualizationSettings": {
        "chartSettings": {
          "gapPolicy": "connect"
        },
        "singleValue": {
          "showLabel": true,
          "label": "",
